==Trivia==
*During his travels before finding the [[Imcando dwarf|Imcando dwarves]], he came across a house in the mist, the figures he comes across seemingly allude to [[Guthix]], [[Saradomin]], and [[Zamorak]], and a number of other figures that could represent other minor [[Gods]]. Their argument reflects Zamorak and Saradomin breaking the [[Edicts of Guthix]] and regaining influence whilst Guthix slept.
*Arrav’s shield remains depicted on the official coins of Varrock to this day as testament to his greatness.{{CiteGodLetter|issue=13|letter=15|title=Guthix Maintains|url={{fullurl:Transcript:Guthix Maintains}}}}
*He is referenced in a letter from the [[Wise Old Man]] to [[Thurgo]] the Imcando dwarf.{{CiteNPC|npc=Dionysius|loc=Old man's message|quote=Following your request, I have spend some time re-reading the relevant scrolls in the Library of Varrock. It appears that when your forefathers encountered that adventurer, he was on a quest to find a mysterious shield.}}

